星、台積電或展訊通信的芯片產品。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/html/it/355763.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2Fhtml%2Fit%2F355763.htm&d=kJKF5bKJ3bb1eMIg7r1iL4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=747da991\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/html/it/355763.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T14:39:12.000Z","msg":"咁ANDROID有咩代替品？"},{"pid":"ab0824543a48ef23bb5f2f146cab45d09d76fe22","tid":632622,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"847f0259322c7744fdf2d0d023673f7e99832c40","tid":632622,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T14:37:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/04/28/taiwan-export-control-zte/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2Ftaiwan-export-control-zte%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=kJKF5bKJ3bb1eMIg7r1iL4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=cf1fe11e\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/04/28/taiwan-export-control-zte/fun-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\n連台灣都向中興宣戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n台灣迫住聽美國話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T14:41:15.000Z","msg":"半個月唔夠已經可以bin C"},{"pid":"6ef80efd148fbf1097f185b249326b2a17122571","tid":632622,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T14:43:09.000Z","msg":"老魔是咪反到short 左"}]}